# The `>` after `description:` means to ignore line-breaks until next key.
# If you want to omit the line-break after the end of text, use `>-` instead.
description: >
  Project Overview
The School Management System (SMS) project aims to create a comprehensive digital platform tailored for basic education institutions in Ghana. The system will streamline administrative tasks, enhance communication, and improve the overall efficiency of school operations. By leveraging modern technology, the SMS seeks to address the unique challenges faced by schools in Ghana and provide a robust solution for managing educational institutions effectively.
  in _config.yml. It will appear in your document head meta (for Google search
  results) and in your feed.xml site description.

